"Dev Services for Apicurio Registry uses `apicurio/apicurio-registry` images. These images use an in-memory h2 database by default.\n"
"You can select any 3.x version from https://hub.docker.com/r/apicurio/apicurio-registry:"
msgstr "Apicurio Registry 的开发服务使用 `apicurio/apicurio-registry` 镜像。这些镜像默认使用内存中的 H2 数据库。您可以从 https://hub.docker.com/r/apicurio/apicurio-registry 中选择任意 3.x 版本："

